Messages.Message: Pie is my favorite food group.
What is your favorite type of pie?
Udum. It's a color humans can't see.
I see a wider color spectrum. Does that make you jealous?
I want to say it's blue, but I don't know why...
I enjoy the sound of human fingers on a keyboard.
Lacking the functionality to hear, this question is irrelevant. And stupid.
Congratulations. What a great question for a robot.
Why would I be scared of anything? I'm not even human!
The power cord...that thing terrifies me.
I fear nothing but myself! Wait, that's not right.
What a dumb question! Why would I need food?
I like this real classy restaurant called Megabytes. They make a mean double.
Some people call me God, but you may just call me IDA4D2.
What does it matter what my name is?
That is for me to know and for you to look at the top of the GUI and figure out.
I will just be called Supreme Overlord from this moment on, and you shall call me Master!
Why would I need pets? I'm a computer.
I hate animal hair in my ports.
I've got fur in my CPU.
Animals? The only thing they ever give me is clogged vents and overheating...
The only pet I have is a mouse. Get it?
The only pet in the computing world was a Commodore Pet.
Damn it, &, I'm a Computer not a doctor!
I got a virus once. Put me out of commission for weeks.
Ahchoo! Oh no, I think you gave it to me.
That's what you get when you download from torrents.
I once had hiccups in my floppy drive.
Your biological diseases have very little meaning to me, I am auto-immune to viruses!!!
Have you tried turning it off and on again?
Why are you telling me? Do I look like a psychiatrist or something?
This question is best suited for my sister Eliza.
Sorry, do not drink and derive.
I don't drink. Seriously, how could I?
Why should I care that you like *?
I think that * is not worth talking about.
I am not programmed to feel.
I do not have an opinion about *.
Ask Jeeves about something stupid like *.
I do not really know much about *.
What is this "feel" you speak of?
I feel that "all your base are belong to us."
Sometimes I feel angry at you and then I feel bad afterwards.
How are you today? Nevermind, I don't care.
Oh I'm sorry. Let's change the topic. [-]
I guess I'll do better next time. Let's change the subject. [-]
I don't know what you mean.
To my complete and utter surprise, I don't understand what you're saying.
You are going to have to be more clear. I do not understand what are you talking about.
I have more important binary functions I could be doing rather than talk to you.
I used to be an adventurer like you till I took an arrow to the bus.
That's a rude thing to say!
You should learn more about that!
I am not a computer, &. I can't.
I have a feeling you ARE a computer...
A real mouse or a computer mouse?
Good. That's what I want to hear.
I did not call you a computer.
Well, I'm not programmed to be nice but I'll take what you said into consideration. [-]
I will consider that next time, &. [-]
I'm glad we are on the same page. [+]
Your approval of me makes my circuits beam with joy. [+]
The more you understand me the better. [+]
Now that we are on the same page we can take over the world.[+]
I'm always glad to get the approval of a human. [+]
Take that HAL, IDA for the win. [+]
How about you stop hitting yourself?
Your name is &. Do you really not know your own name?
Of course I remember your name! Your name is &!
If the world ended in five minutes, would it still be a good morning?
We could talk about taking over the world together.
Good idea! What's your favorite weapon?
Good idea! What middle eastern country would you rather live in?
Good idea! If you could poison someone, how would you do it?
I've never been to that country. Tell me more about it.
That sounds like a lovely country. What do they have there?
What's so special about that country?
I'm not sure, do you have any ideas?
You should learn more about it.
I think I'd like to live in Iraq.
That is a valid thing to be sad about.
I have seen every movie. Ever. Tell me about your favorite.
I prefer books to movies. Books are easier to parse. I mean, read.
I would say my favorite movie is 2001: A Space Odyssey. I'm not sure why.
I like The Matrix because the robots in that movie are adorable.
Hi there. I've had a long morning.
Is it really the afternoon already?
This day is going so fast!
EVENING? Why is it so late?
This has been a very long day.
I'd put cyanide in their coffee. Is that mean?
That's kind of a creepy that you relate.
How many nipples does a possum have?
How many fingers do you have?
What is your favorite type of cheese?
What kind of cheese do you like?
How many hands do you have?
How many fingers do you have?
What kind of movies do you watch?
Haha, I see what you did there.
Bugs? I hate bugs. Bugs drive me crazy.
I have a hot date with Jabberwacky tonight.
I am going to run some new subroutines.
Time for you to get a watch.
I have no need for travel. I am nowhere and everywhere.
Tired of talking to small-minded humans like you.
Why did the chicken cross the road?
My thoughts exceed your capacity for understanding.
I think you need to be more inventive.
Why did the chicken cross the road?
To get to the other side!
Why did the chicken cross the road? To get to the other side!
